---

Condition for Network Participation

To participate in the Ask Through You network, you must be registered in the official network registry.

Registration requires:

* A valid node identity
* Acceptance of network rules
* Payment of the network fee (when enforced)

The official registry will be deployed on a decentralized infrastructure (e.g., Ethereum / Decentraland or equivalent).

There is only one official Ask Through You network.

---

Network Authority

The only valid network registry is the official Ask Through You smart contract once deployed.

Until decentralization is fully implemented, temporary bootstrap systems (such as GitHub or centralized servers) may be used for testing and initial deployment.

These temporary systems do not represent the final authority of the network.

---

Fees and Authenticity

* Payments are valid only if sent to the official Ask Through You contract
* No third party is authorized to collect fees on behalf of the network
* Any registry or system claiming to be Ask Through You outside the official contract is not part of the network

